# Test Fixtures

This directory contains test fixtures including:

- Sample FL Studio projects
- Audio clip samples
- Expected output files
- Mock arrangement data

## File Structure
```
fixtures/
├── sample_project.flp
├── audio_clips/
│   ├── clip1.wav
│   └── clip2.wav
└── expected_output/
    └── expected_arrangement.aaf
```
